* Why Implement\nForeign Catalogs?
** Governance & auditability
***_ Policies defined once in Unity Catalog
***_ Audit logs for all foreign data access
***_ No separate permission management
** External data access without ETL
***_ Proof-of-concept on live data
***_ Ad hoc reports from operational systems
***_ Data quality validation before migration
** Incremental migration support
***_ Access un-migrated legacy data
***_ Gradual transition, not cutover
@endmindmap
